HEADWORD: Histonomy
<hw>His*ton"o*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>"isto`s</grk> tissue + <?/ to distribute, regulate.]</ety> <def>The
